data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Hunter's Crossing. Large eat-in kitchen with slider door to spacious back yard. Large family room off kitchen. Formal Dining area and living room. Huge loft upstairs. Fenced in back yard with gazebo and pool. Roof replaced in 2015. New front picture window and sliders to the back yard. AC was replaced 5 years ago. Water heater is 3 years old. appliances stay! Channahon community offers ponds, walking/biking paths and playgrounds in the neighborhood.
